josh weinstein ( born may 21 , 1971https://twitter.com/jelvisweinstein/status/337050096359321600 ) , later known as j. elvis weinstein , is an american writer and performer , best known for his roles as dr. laurence erhardt and the original puppeteer and voice for tom servo and gypsy on mystery science theater 3000 .

writing for tv : before writing for " afv " & " freaks and geeks " , j. elvis weinstein was the original voice of tom servo on this cult classic

